The paper discusses Transactional Memory (TM), which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also introduces a new safety property for TM, which falls under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper presents an algorithm that satisfies the new safety property, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE).
